967
00:57:42.043 --> 00:57:43.633
If you need any further information,

968
00:57:44.087 --> 00:57:46.417
it's available online. Thank you.

969
00:57:49.676 --> 00:57:51.466
Fuck's sake.

970
00:58:13.783 --> 00:58:15.793
- Hello?
